<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Size Uygun Gayrimenkuller | Portföy AI</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #2A60FF;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header img {
      max-width: 150px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #F5F6FA;
    }
    .property-item {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 5px;
      padding: 15px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .property-item img {
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    .property-details {
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #30C98E;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <img src="{{companyLogo}}" alt="{{companyName}} Logo">
      <h1>Size Uygun Gayrimenkuller</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <p>Sayın {{buyerName}},</p>
      
      <div class="ai-response">
        {{{emailContent}}}
      </div>
      
      <h2>Size Özel Seçilmiş Gayrimenkuller</h2>
      
      {{#each properties}}
      <div class="property-item">
        <div class="property-details">
          <h3>{{this.propertyType}} - {{this.location}}</h3>
          <p><strong>Fiyat:</strong> {{this.price}} {{this.currency}}</p>
          <p><strong>Oda Sayısı:</strong> {{this.roomCount}}</p>
          <p><strong>Metrekare:</strong> {{this.size}} m²</p>
          <p>{{this.description}}</p>
          <a href="mailto:{{../contactEmail}}?subject=İlan%20No:%20{{this.listingNo}}" class="cta-button">Detaylı Bilgi Al</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      {{/each}}
      
      <p>Görüntüleme randevusu oluşturmak veya daha fazla bilgi almak için bizimle iletişime geçebilirsiniz.</p>
      
      <p>Saygılarımızla,<br>
      {{companyName}} Ekibi</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>{{companyName}}</p>
      <p>Telefon: {{contactPhone}} | E-posta: {{contactEmail}}</p>
      <p>Bu e-posta size özel gönderilmiştir. Lütfen yanıtlamayınız.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 